fsw_command.description: This command combines instrument commands UVS_MODE_SAFE, UVS_MODE_DECON, and UVS_MODE_CHECKOUT. This command sets the operational state of UVS to SAFE, DECON or CHECKOUT mode. Transition to SAFE more is unconditional.
